## Terrafrom Language **
- Syntax:
   Key = value
- No Indentation Specific. {} to define blocks.
- HashoCope Configuration Language.
- Terraform configuration file
- .tf / .tf.json
- Block Specfiy.

- Provider "<PROVIDER-NAME>" {}
- resource "<RESOURCE-TYPE>" "<RESOURCE-NAME>" {}
- data
- variable 
- output
- module 
